{
  "video_id": "Cprp_EjVtwA",
  "title": "Why I train grandmothers to treat depression | Dixon Chibanda",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12813.0,
      "end_time": 15579.0,
      "text": "On a warm August morning in Harare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16335.0,
      "end_time": 17500.0,
      "text": "Farai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18550.0,
      "end_time": 21120.0,
      "text": "a 24-year-old mother of two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21144.0,
      "end_time": 23863.0,
      "text": "walks towards a park bench."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24765.0,
      "end_time": 28790.0,
      "text": "She looks miserable and dejected."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28581.0,
      "end_time": 33904.0,
      "text": "Now, on the park bench sits an 82-year-old woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33928.0,
      "end_time": 37477.0,
      "text": "better known to the community as Grandmother Jack."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39392.0,
      "end_time": 45912.0,
      "text": "Farai hands Grandmother Jack an envelope from the clinic nurse."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 47373.0,
      "end_time": 50385.0,
      "text": "Grandmother Jack invites Farai to sit down"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50409.0,
      "end_time": 53793.0,
      "text": "as she opens the envelope and reads."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53817.0,
      "end_time": 57664.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s silence for three minutes or so as she reads."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58899.0,
      "end_time": 62965.0,
      "text": "And after a long pause, Grandmother Jack takes a deep breath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62989.0,
      "end_time": 65501.0,
      "text": "looks at Farai and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 66640.0,
      "end_time": 67926.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m here for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 70463.0,
      "end_time": 72615.0,
      "text": "Would you like to share your story with me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 73530.0,
      "end_time": 75368.0,
      "text": "Farai begins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 75392.0,
      "end_time": 77898.0,
      "text": "her eyes swelling with tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 79383.0,
      "end_time": 81443.0,
      "text": "She says, \"Grandmother Jack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82920.0,
      "end_time": 83756.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m HIV-positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84721.0,
      "end_time": 87587.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been living with HIV for the past four years."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 88190.0,
      "end_time": 90208.0,
      "text": "My husband left me a year ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90645.0,
      "end_time": 91943.0,
      "text": "I have two kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92683.0,
      "end_time": 94130.0,
      "text": "under the age of five."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94343.0,
      "end_time": 95538.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m unemployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95981.0,
      "end_time": 99542.0,
      "text": "I can hardly take care of my children.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100211.0,
      "end_time": 102714.0,
      "text": "Tears are now flowing down her face."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103252.0,
      "end_time": 106732.0,
      "text": "And in response, Grandmother Jack moves closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107375.0,
      "end_time": 109329.0,
      "text": "puts her hand on Farai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109353.0,
      "end_time": 112538.0,
      "text": "and says, \"Farai, it&#39;s OK to cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 115256.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve been through a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116453.0,
      "end_time": 118401.0,
      "text": "Would you like to share more with me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119600.0,
      "end_time": 120747.0,
      "text": "And Farai continues."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122140.0,
      "end_time": 123841.0,
      "text": "\"In the last three weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 124666.0,
      "end_time": 128413.0,
      "text": "I have had recurrent thoughts of killing myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129603.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131608.0,
      "text": "taking my two children with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132717.0,
      "end_time": 134343.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t take it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135154.0,
      "end_time": 139222.0,
      "text": "The clinic nurse sent me to see you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 140304.0,
      "end_time": 144528.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an exchange between the two, which lasts about 30 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 145128.0,
      "end_time": 147684.0,
      "text": "And finally, Grandmother Jack says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148569.0,
      "end_time": 149726.0,
      "text": "\"Farai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150533.0,
      "end_time": 156280.0,
      "text": "it seems to me that you have all the symptoms of kufungisisa.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 157778.0,
      "end_time": 162543.0,
      "text": "The word \"kufungisisa\" opens up a floodgate of tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164497.0,
      "end_time": 168753.0,
      "text": "So, kufungisisa is the local equivalent of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168777.0,
      "end_time": 169927.0,
      "text": "in my country."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 170776.0,
      "end_time": 172363.0,
      "text": "It literally means"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 172837.0,
      "end_time": 174578.0,
      "text": "\"thinking too much.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 176350.0,
      "end_time": 179444.0,
      "text": "The World Health Organization estimates"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179468.0,
      "end_time": 185577.0,
      "text": "that more than 300 million people globally, today, suffer from depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185601.0,
      "end_time": 188473.0,
      "text": "or what in my country we call kufungisisa."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188966.0,
      "end_time": 192120.0,
      "text": "And the World Health Organization also tells us"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 192360.0,
      "end_time": 195153.0,
      "text": "that every 40 seconds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195177.0,
      "end_time": 199227.0,
      "text": "someone somewhere in the world commits suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 199251.0,
      "end_time": 200522.0,
      "text": "because they are unhappy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 201550.0,
      "end_time": 204612.0,
      "text": "largely due to depression or kufungisisa."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 204636.0,
      "end_time": 208216.0,
      "text": "And most of these deaths are occurring in low- and middle-income countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 209395.0,
      "end_time": 210621.0,
      "text": "In fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 210645.0,
      "end_time": 213548.0,
      "text": "the World Health Organization goes as far as to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 214425.0,
      "end_time": 218333.0,
      "text": "that when you look at the age group between 15 to 29,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 218357.0,
      "end_time": 222805.0,
      "text": "a leading cause of death now is actually suicide."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 223849.0,
      "end_time": 227505.0,
      "text": "But there are wider events that lead to depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 227529.0,
      "end_time": 229323.0,
      "text": "and in some cases, suicide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 229348.0,
      "end_time": 230634.0,
      "text": "such as abuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 231151.0,
      "end_time": 233194.0,
      "text": "conflict, violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 233865.0,
      "end_time": 236208.0,
      "text": "isolation, loneliness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236232.0,
      "end_time": 237583.0,
      "text": "the list is endless."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239594.0,
      "end_time": 241910.0,
      "text": "But one thing that we do know"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 241934.0,
      "end_time": 245883.0,
      "text": "is that depression can be treated and suicides averted."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 246401.0,
      "end_time": 247557.0,
      "text": "But the problem is"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 247581.0,
      "end_time": 251300.0,
      "text": "we just don&#39;t have enough psychiatrists or psychologists in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 251550.0,
      "end_time": 252413.0,
      "text": "to do the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252437.0,
      "end_time": 255461.0,
      "text": "In most low- and middle-income countries, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255485.0,
      "end_time": 258265.0,
      "text": "the ratio of psychiatrists to the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258289.0,
      "end_time": 262449.0,
      "text": "is something like one for every one and a half million people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262473.0,
      "end_time": 266500.0,
      "text": "which literally means that 90 percent of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 266740.0,
      "end_time": 268940.0,
      "text": "needing mental health services"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 268118.0,
      "end_time": 269606.0,
      "text": "will not get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270390.0,
      "end_time": 271229.0,
      "text": "In my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 271918.0,
      "end_time": 274547.0,
      "text": "there are 12 psychiatrists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 274571.0,
      "end_time": 275815.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m one of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276414.0,
      "end_time": 280328.0,
      "text": "for a population of approximately 14 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 280352.0,
      "end_time": 282342.0,
      "text": "Now, let me just put that into context."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 283107.0,
      "end_time": 285759.0,
      "text": "One evening while I was at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 286319.0,
      "end_time": 288967.0,
      "text": "I get a call from the ER,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288991.0,
      "end_time": 290514.0,
      "text": "or the emergency room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291308.0,
      "end_time": 294327.0,
      "text": "from a city which is some 200 kilometers away"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294908.0,
      "end_time": 296173.0,
      "text": "from where I live."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 296197.0,
      "end_time": 297845.0,
      "text": "And the ER doctor says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 297869.0,
      "end_time": 299580.0,
      "text": "\"One of your patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299820.0,
      "end_time": 300956.0,
      "text": "someone you treated four months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301440.0,
      "end_time": 303172.0,
      "text": "has just taken an overdose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 303196.0,
      "end_time": 305245.0,
      "text": "and they are in the ER department."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 305673.0,
      "end_time": 307809.0,
      "text": "Hemodynamically, they seem to be OK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 307833.0,
      "end_time": 311595.0,
      "text": "but they will need neuropsychiatric evaluation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 311619.0,
      "end_time": 314944.0,
      "text": "Now, I obviously can&#39;t get into my car in the middle of the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 314968.0,
      "end_time": 316689.0,
      "text": "and drive 200 kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 316713.0,
      "end_time": 318959.0,
      "text": "So as best as we could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318983.0,
      "end_time": 321395.0,
      "text": "over the phone with the ER doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 321419.0,
      "end_time": 323681.0,
      "text": "we come up with an assessment."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 324148.0,
      "end_time": 328662.0,
      "text": "We ensure that suicidal observations are in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 329162.0,
      "end_time": 332409.0,
      "text": "We ensure that we start reviewing the antidepressants"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 332434.0,
      "end_time": 334698.0,
      "text": "that this patient has been taking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 334722.0,
      "end_time": 336534.0,
      "text": "and we finally conclude"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 337360.0,
      "end_time": 340757.0,
      "text": "that as soon as Erica -- that was her name, 26-year-old --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340781.0,
      "end_time": 344694.0,
      "text": "as soon as Erica is ready to be released from the ER,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344718.0,
      "end_time": 347328.0,
      "text": "she should come directly to me with her mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347352.0,
      "end_time": 349303.0,
      "text": "and I will evaluate"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 349327.0,
      "end_time": 351118.0,
      "text": "and establish what can be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351142.0,
      "end_time": 353884.0,
      "text": "And we assumed that that would take about a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 354994.0,
      "end_time": 356404.0,
      "text": "A week passes."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 356428.0,
      "end_time": 357578.0,
      "text": "Three weeks pass."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357884.0,
      "end_time": 359830.0,
      "text": "No Erica."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 359558.0,
      "end_time": 361921.0,
      "text": "And one day I get a call from Erica&#39;s mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 362488.0,
      "end_time": 363704.0,
      "text": "and she says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 364853.0,
      "end_time": 367319.0,
      "text": "\"Erica committed suicide three days ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 367894.0,
      "end_time": 371760.0,
      "text": "She hanged herself from the mango tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 372645.0,
      "end_time": 374103.0,
      "text": "in the family garden.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 376417.0,
      "end_time": 379114.0,
      "text": "Now, almost like a knee-jerk reaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 379614.0,
      "end_time": 381887.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t help but ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 381911.0,
      "end_time": 385190.0,
      "text": "\"But why didn&#39;t you come to Harare, where I live?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 385430.0,
      "end_time": 388212.0,
      "text": "We had agreed that as soon as you&#39;re released from the ER,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 388236.0,
      "end_time": 389505.0,
      "text": "you will come to me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 390290.0,
      "end_time": 392488.0,
      "text": "Her response was brief."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 394560.0,
      "end_time": 397628.0,
      "text": "\"We didn&#39;t have the 15 dollars bus fare"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 397652.0,
      "end_time": 398918.0,
      "text": "to come to Harare.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400412.0,
      "end_time": 404203.0,
      "text": "Now, suicide is not an unusual event"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 404228.0,
      "end_time": 406145.0,
      "text": "in the world of mental health."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 407101.0,
      "end_time": 409724.0,
      "text": "But there was something about Erica&#39;s death"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 409748.0,
      "end_time": 412894.0,
      "text": "that struck me at the core of my very being."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 414367.0,
      "end_time": 417182.0,
      "text": "That statement from Erica&#39;s mother:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 417766.0,
      "end_time": 422198.0,
      "text": "\"We didn&#39;t have 15 dollars bus fare to come to you,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 423103.0,
      "end_time": 424768.0,
      "text": "made me realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 425784.0,
      "end_time": 427925.0,
      "text": "that it just wasn&#39;t going to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 427949.0,
      "end_time": 430457.0,
      "text": "me expecting people to come to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 430813.0,
      "end_time": 434546.0,
      "text": "And I got into this state of soul-searching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434570.0,
      "end_time": 438175.0,
      "text": "trying to really discover my role"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 438199.0,
      "end_time": 441228.0,
      "text": "as a psychiatrist in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 441252.0,
      "end_time": 445799.0,
      "text": "And after considerable consultation and soul-searching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 445823.0,
      "end_time": 448926.0,
      "text": "talking to colleagues, friends and family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 448951.0,
      "end_time": 451820.0,
      "text": "it suddenly dawned on me"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 451106.0,
      "end_time": 456243.0,
      "text": "that actually, one the most reliable resources we have in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 456892.0,
      "end_time": 458177.0,
      "text": "are grandmothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 459707.0,
      "end_time": 461272.0,
      "text": "Yes, grandmothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 461661.0,
      "end_time": 462904.0,
      "text": "And I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 463753.0,
      "end_time": 466147.0,
      "text": "grandmothers are in every community."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 466171.0,
      "end_time": 467764.0,
      "text": "There are hundreds of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 468183.0,
      "end_time": 469349.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 469373.0,
      "end_time": 470582.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 470607.0,
      "end_time": 475967.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t leave their communities in search of greener pastures."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 475991.0,
      "end_time": 477188.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 477495.0,
      "end_time": 479150.0,
      "text": "See, the only time they leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 479390.0,
      "end_time": 481608.0,
      "text": "is when they go to a greener pasture called heaven."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 481632.0,
      "end_time": 482756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 482780.0,
      "end_time": 485743.0,
      "text": "So I thought, how about training grandmothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486740.0,
      "end_time": 489680.0,
      "text": "in evidence-based talk therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 489704.0,
      "end_time": 492806.0,
      "text": "which they can deliver on a bench?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493283.0,
      "end_time": 496180.0,
      "text": "Empower them with the skills to listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 496966.0,
      "end_time": 498278.0,
      "text": "to show empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 499154.0,
      "end_time": 502514.0,
      "text": "all of that rooted in cognitive behavioral therapy;"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502538.0,
      "end_time": 507200.0,
      "text": "empower them with the skills to provide behavior activation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 507440.0,
      "end_time": 508876.0,
      "text": "activity scheduling;"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 508900.0,
      "end_time": 513472.0,
      "text": "and support them using digital technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513496.0,
      "end_time": 515589.0,
      "text": "You know, mobile phone technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 515614.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518246.00000000006,
      "text": "Pretty much everyone in Africa has a mobile phone today."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 518871.0,
      "end_time": 520636.0,
      "text": "So in 2006,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 520659.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522839.99999999994,
      "text": "I started my first group"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524150.0,
      "end_time": 525300.0,
      "text": "of grandmothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 525324.0,
      "end_time": 528846.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529186.0,
      "end_time": 530336.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 530360.0,
      "end_time": 532639.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 533229.0,
      "end_time": 536564.0,
      "text": "Today, there are hundreds of grandmothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 536588.0,
      "end_time": 539384.0,
      "text": "who are working in more than 70 communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 540844.0,
      "end_time": 542672.0,
      "text": "And in the last year alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 543371.0,
      "end_time": 548295.0,
      "text": "more than 30,000 people received treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 548320.0,
      "end_time": 549837.0,
      "text": "on the Friendship Bench"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549861.0,
      "end_time": 553228.0,
      "text": "from a grandmother in a community in Zimbabwe."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 553745.0,
      "end_time": 556705.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 561305.0,
      "end_time": 566275.0,
      "text": "And recently, we published this work that is done by these grandmothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 566299.0,
      "end_time": 569361.0,
      "text": "in the Journal of the American Medical Association."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 569385.0,
      "end_time": 570535.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 570559.0,
      "end_time": 572217.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 572241.0,
      "end_time": 578918.0,
      "text": "And our results show that six months after receiving treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 578942.0,
      "end_time": 580169.0,
      "text": "from a grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 580685.0,
      "end_time": 582423.0,
      "text": "people were still symptom-free:"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 582851.0,
      "end_time": 584610.0,
      "text": "no depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 584836.0,
      "end_time": 587238.0,
      "text": "suicidal ideation completely reduced."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 587262.0,
      "end_time": 590944.0,
      "text": "In fact, our results -- this was a clinical trial --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 590968.0,
      "end_time": 592949.0,
      "text": "in fact, this clinical trial showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 592973.0,
      "end_time": 596220.0,
      "text": "that grandmothers were more effective at treating depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 596470.0,
      "end_time": 597246.0,
      "text": "than doctors and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597270.0,
      "end_time": 598808.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 598832.0,
      "end_time": 602139.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 606466.0,
      "end_time": 607685.0,
      "text": "And so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 608764.0,
      "end_time": 612200.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re now working towards expanding this program."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614794.0,
      "end_time": 621473.0,
      "text": "There are more than 600 million people currently aged above 65 in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 621813.0,
      "end_time": 623684.0,
      "text": "And by the year 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 623708.0,
      "end_time": 628415.0,
      "text": "there will be 1.5 billion people aged 65 and above."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 629455.0,
      "end_time": 635473.0,
      "text": "Imagine if we could create a global network of grandmothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 635497.0,
      "end_time": 639858.0,
      "text": "in every major city in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 639883.0,
      "end_time": 643994.0,
      "text": "who are trained in evidence-based talk therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 644180.0,
      "end_time": 646578.0,
      "text": "supported through digital platforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 646602.0,
      "end_time": 647817.0,
      "text": "networked."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 648553.0,
      "end_time": 652946.0,
      "text": "And they will make a difference in communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 653377.0,
      "end_time": 655602.0,
      "text": "They will reduce the treatment gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 655626.0,
      "end_time": 658792.0,
      "text": "for mental, neurological and substance-use disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 660283.0,
      "end_time": 661563.0,
      "text": "Finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 661587.0,
      "end_time": 665115.0,
      "text": "this is a file photograph of Grandmother Jack."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 665842.0,
      "end_time": 671564.0,
      "text": "So, Farai had six sessions on the bench with Grandmother Jack."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 672890.0,
      "end_time": 673955.0,
      "text": "Today, Farai is employed."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 674463.0,
      "end_time": 677887.0,
      "text": "She has her two children at school."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 678668.0,
      "end_time": 680149.0,
      "text": "And as for Grandmother Jack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 680786.0,
      "end_time": 686936.0,
      "text": "one morning in February, we expected her to see her 257th client on the bench."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 688453.0,
      "end_time": 689828.0,
      "text": "She didn&#39;t show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 691760.0,
      "end_time": 694100.0,
      "text": "She had gone to a greener pasture called heaven."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 694460.0,
      "end_time": 697717.0,
      "text": "But I believe that Grandmother Jack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 697741.0,
      "end_time": 698970.0,
      "text": "from up there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 699719.0,
      "end_time": 702185.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s cheering on all the other grandmothers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 702209.0,
      "end_time": 706801.0,
      "text": "the increasing number of grandmothers who are making a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 706826.0,
      "end_time": 709330.0,
      "text": "in the lives of thousands of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 710118.0,
      "end_time": 712627.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sure she&#39;s in awe"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 712651.0,
      "end_time": 717500.0,
      "text": "when she realizes that something that she helped to pioneer"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 717524.0,
      "end_time": 720128.0,
      "text": "is now spreading to other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 720152.0,
      "end_time": 721374.0,
      "text": "like Malawi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 721398.0,
      "end_time": 722866.0,
      "text": "the island of Zanzibar"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 722890.0,
      "end_time": 726501.0,
      "text": "and coming closer to home here in the Unites States"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 726525.0,
      "end_time": 727982.0,
      "text": "in the city of New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 729390.0,
      "end_time": 731379.0,
      "text": "May her soul rest in peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 732508.0,
      "end_time": 733663.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 733687.0,
      "end_time": 736480.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 736504.0,
      "end_time": 738489.0,
      "text": "(Cheering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738513.0,
      "end_time": 740399.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}